1.title: To Raw #1083
1.plot: Host Josh Mathews is joined by Alex Riley, Booker T. Huffman Jr. and Jimmy Hart live from Resch Center in Green Bay, Wisconsin U.S.A. to preview WWE Monday Night Raw #1083.

2.title: To Raw #1084
2.plot: Host Josh Mathews and professional wrestling analysts Alex Riley, Booker T. Huffman and "Hacksaw" Jim Duggan are live from Allstate Arena in Rosemont, Illinois U.S.A. to preview WWE Monday Night Raw #1084.

3.title: To Raw #1085
3.plot: Host Josh Mathews and WWE analysts Alex Riley, Booker T. Huffman Jr. and Jimmy Hart are live from FedExForum in Memphis, Tennessee U.S.A. to preview WWE Monday Night Raw #1085; Renee Young interviews Sheamus; and much more.
